SQL query of the view VDAR_DAR_DADO_RELATORIO

SELECT DAR.DAR_ID, DAR.REL_ID, DAR.DAR_DS_CHAVE, DAR.DAR_AN_CONTEUDO, DAR.DAR_CD_ORDEM, DAR.DAR_CD_STATUS, DAR.MDR_ID
FROM SUP.DAR_DADO_RELATORIO DAR
INNER JOIN SUP.REL_RELATORIO_APS REL ON DAR.REL_ID = REL.REL_ID
INNER JOIN SUP.INE_INSPECAO_ENTIDADE INE ON INE.INE_ID = REL.INE_ID
WHERE INE.INE_CD_STATUS = 3
AND (INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO >= '2015-01-01' AND INE.INE_DH_PUBLICACAO < '2018-01-01')
